  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Billing & Payment Terms</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Last updated: August 2025</p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    I send <span class="font-semibold">one flat, annual invoice</span> based on team size. <span class="font-semibold">No metering. No auto-renewal.</span> Try it for a quarter.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    You will receive a <span class="font-semibold">pre-signed</span> <a href="/msa.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-semibold">MSA</a> (and optional <a href="/dpa.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline font-semibold">DPA</a>) via DocuSign a month in. <span class="font-semibold">No redlines.</span> I'll backdate your invoice to the start of whatever month you sign. <span class="font-semibold">Net 30</span> payment window.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-6">
    Invoices are emailed (via Stripe) with <span class="font-semibold">full remittance details</span>. Pay by <span class="font-semibold">card</span>, <span class="font-semibold">ACH</span>, or <span class="font-semibold">wire</span>.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-10">
    Or simply unsubscribe. The emails stop after a quarter, and your data gets wiped automatically.
  </p>

