    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 75 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$20,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 150 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$40,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 300 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$80,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 border-b border-gray-100"><div class="px-4 py-2">Up to 1,000 engineers</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$100,000</div></div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2"><div class="px-4 py-2">Unlimited Usage</div><div class="px-4 py-2">$200,000</div></div>
  </div>

  <p class="mb-10 text-sm text-center">
    Pre-pay future years for <span class="font-semibold">20%</span> off today's prices. Email <a href="mailto:procurement@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">procurement@replicate.info</a> for an invoice.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-semibold">Your price is fixed for the year</p>
  <p class="mb-4">Just one fixed, non-refundable annual invoice (Net 30). If the team grows past your current tier, great, they can still use the product. Just renew at a higher tier next year. No mid-year surprises.</p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-semibold">Renewal Process</p>
  <p class="mb-4">I'll email you 30 days before term end. Renewals require explicit confirmation from an administrator. You will not receive an invoice unless you choose to continue, every year.</p>

  <p class="font-medium mb-1">Sales Tax</p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Sales tax (e.g., VAT, GST, US state) is calculated at checkout (if applicable) via <a href="https://stripe.com/tax" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Stripe Tax</a>. If your organization is tax-exempt, simply email <a href="mailto:procurement@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">procurement@replicate.info</a> with your exemption certificate, and I'll apply it before sending over your first invoice.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-medium">Refund Policy</p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    I don't offer refunds once an invoice is paid, even if usage stops. Happy to help fix erroneous payments.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-1 font-medium">Support</p>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Email support is included for all tiers via <a href="mailto:support@replicate.info" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@replicate.info</a>. Typical response time is 1-2 days.
  </p>

  <h3 class="font-medium mt-4 mb-1">Insurance Coverage</h3>
  <p>Replicate Software, LLC maintains $1M <a href="/coi.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Errors & Omissions</a> and $1M <a href="/coi.pdf" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Cyber Liability</a> coverage via <a href="https://vouch.us" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Vouch</a>.</p>

